These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: funk, d&b, salsa, electronic, pop, punk
6 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, hamster, turtle, bird, horse
 1. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
 3. the fan of pop is not the owner of the bird##6
 4. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
 5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 7. the owner of the bird is not the fan of d&b##6
 8. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of funk is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the fan of electronic##7
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
11. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
12. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
13. the owner of the fish is the fan of funk##1
14. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
15. the fan of punk is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | funk | salsa   | punk     | d&b    | pop   |
| Pet           | bird | fish   | horse | turtle | hamster | chinchilla |

