.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: western, comedy, animation, adventure, musical, scientific
6 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, cat, hamster, frog, goat
 1. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 7. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
 8. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching musical movies is not the owner of the frog##6
10. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##7
11. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
12. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
13. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
14. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
15. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
16. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
17. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the person watching musical movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | scientific | adventure | musical     | animation      | western |
| Pet           | lizard         | cat        | frog   | hamster | ferret | goat    |

