.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, coffee, almond-milk, 7up
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing, climbing, soccer, ice-hockey, 7up-polo
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is not the person drinking coffee##6
 5. the person drinking juice is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is 7up-polo##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking mirinda##7
11. the person who's sport is 7up-polo is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
13. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
14. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is 7up-polo##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk        | coffee | 7up    | juice    | sprite | mirinda |
| Sport      | sailing | ice-hockey  | 7up-polo | soccer | biathlon | climbing      |

