The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: scientific, zombie, adventure, documentary, disaster, animation
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 6. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking iced-tea##7
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking fanta##7
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking juice##7
10. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
13. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking juice##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Beverage      | juice | sprite | fanta | tea | iced-tea | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | documentary      | scientific | disaster     | animation | zombie |

