 9. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the person driving the bike##7
13. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | frog   | horse | guinea-pig      | pony | mouse  | snake   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | roller  | bike | van   | taxi | airplane |

