.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: woodworking, reading, writing, singing, filmmaking, chess
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, chef, nurse, security-guard, photographer, architect
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the security-guard and the chef##7
 5. the architect is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is the photographer##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
 8. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
 9. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
10. the chef is somewhere to the right of the architect##5
11. the architect is on the right of the nurse##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
13. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is writing##7
14. the chef is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
15. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | writing         | singing | reading | woodworking   | chess | filmmaking  |
| Job     | photographer | security-guard  | nurse  | architect | chef  | analyst |

 